---
import Layout from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Layout title="Arena — System Logic | Thee Rainers">
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <meta name="description" content="Neural boxing. Systemic performance in motion. Watch the methodology applied — not explained." />
  </Fragment>

  <!-- Featured Video -->
  <section class="bg-white px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24 pt-32 md:pt-40 pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto w-full">

      <div class="mb-12">
        <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[11px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-6">The Arena</p>
        <h1 class="font-black text-[#0A0A0A] uppercase tracking-tighter text-5xl md:text-7xl leading-[0.8] mb-8">Neural boxing.<br/>In motion.</h1>
        <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/40 text-base max-w-[480px] leading-relaxed">The system, applied. Not theory — execution. Watch the methodology in real-time, then decide if this is the architecture you need.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- ── FEATURED VIDEO EMBED ──────────────────────────────────────
           Replace the src attribute with your YouTube or Vimeo embed URL.
           YouTube format: https://www.youtube.com/embed/VIDEO_ID
           Vimeo format:   https://player.vimeo.com/video/VIDEO_ID
      ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
      <div class="relative w-full aspect-video bg-[#F6F6F6] border border-[#0A0A0A]/8 mb-4">
        <iframe
          id="arena-featured-video"
          src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/3N5GgvuvrVo"
          title="Why Boxing Classes Don't Work (And What Actually Does)"
          allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
          allowfullscreen
          class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full"
        ></iframe>
      </div>
      <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/25 text-[11px] tracking-widest uppercase">Featured — Why Structure Beats Volume</p>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 3-Layered Operating System -->
  <section class="bg-white px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24 py-24 border-t border-[#0A0A0A]/8">
    <div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto w-full">

      <div class="mb-20">
        <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[11px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-6">The Operating System</p>
        <h2 class="font-black text-[#0A0A0A] uppercase tracking-tighter text-4xl md:text-5xl leading-[0.85] max-w-[560px]">Three layers.<br/>One integrated<br/>system.</h2>
      </div>

      <!-- Layer 01: Perceptual -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[1fr_3fr] gap-8 md:gap-16 py-12 border-t border-[#0A0A0A]/8 tr-card">
        <div>
          <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-3">Layer 01</p>
          <p class="font-black text-[#0A0A0A] uppercase tracking-tighter text-xl leading-tight">Perceptual<br/>Layer</p>
          <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/25 text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mt-3">Quiet Eye · Cue Reading · Processing Speed</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
          <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/60 text-base leading-relaxed mb-4">The quiet eye is not a relaxed eye — it is a trained one. Cue-reading, threat detection, and processing speed are trainable inputs that most fighters never address. Their body reacts to what their eye has already failed to process.</p>
          <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">When the perceptual layer is trained, the fighter stops reacting and starts operating. Decision time collapses. Execution becomes pre-cognitive. That is the output of Layer 01.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Layer 02: Mechanical -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[1fr_3fr] gap-8 md:gap-16 py-12 border-t border-[#0A0A0A]/8 tr-card">
        <div>
          <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-3">Layer 02</p>
          <p class="font-black text-[#0A0A0A] uppercase tracking-tighter text-xl leading-tight">Mechanical<br/>Layer</p>
          <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/25 text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mt-3">Kinetic Chain · Floor-Up Power · Structural Integrity</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
          <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/60 text-base leading-relaxed mb-4">Force does not originate at the fist. It originates at the floor. The kinetic chain — foot, ankle, knee, hip, torso, shoulder, fist — is either integrated or it is broken. A broken chain produces power loss, injury accumulation, and mechanical fragmentation under pressure.</p>
          <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">Integration produces floor-up force transfer, structural efficiency, and durability across a full camp. This is what the Footwork Protocol addresses at Layer 02. The drill is the diagnostic. The pattern is the fix.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Layer 03: Existential -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[1fr_3fr] gap-8 md:gap-16 py-12 border-t border-[#0A0A0A]/8 tr-card">
        <div>
          <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-3">Layer 03</p>
          <p class="font-black text-[#0A0A0A] uppercase tracking-tighter text-xl leading-tight">Existential<br/>Layer</p>
          <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/25 text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mt-3">Identity · Presence · Internal Standard</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
          <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/60 text-base leading-relaxed mb-4">The final layer cannot be drilled in isolation. It is identity — the non-negotiable operating baseline a fighter maintains regardless of external conditions: the opponent, the crowd, the round, the result. This is not motivation. Motivation is fragile. Identity is structural.</p>
          <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">The fighter who has integrated Layer 03 does not perform when conditions are right. They perform because their identity does not allow otherwise. That is the difference between a fighter who competes and one who executes.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Scripture -->
      <div class="py-16 border-t border-[#0A0A0A]/8">
        <p class="font-black text-[#0A0A0A]/15 uppercase tracking-tighter text-2xl md:text-3xl leading-[0.9] max-w-[680px] mb-6">"I do not run aimlessly. I do not fight like a boxer beating the air. I strike a blow to my body and make it my slave."</p>
        <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase">1 Corinthians 9:26–27</p>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center justify-between gap-8 border-t border-[#0A0A0A]/8 pt-16">
        <div>
          <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/25 text-[11px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-3">Ready to build the system?</p>
          <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/50 text-sm max-w-[440px] leading-relaxed">The Vault gives you the entry point. Private Architecture gives you the full operating system — engineered around you.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 shrink-0">
          <a href="/vault"
            class="blue-btn inline-flex items-center justify-center font-bold border-2 border-[#0057FF] text-[#0057FF] bg-transparent px-10 py-4 text-sm tracking-widest uppercase transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-[#0057FF] hover:text-white">
            Enter the Vault →
          </a>
          <a href="/command"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center font-bold border border-[#0A0A0A]/15 text-[#0A0A0A]/40 bg-transparent px-10 py-4 text-sm tracking-widest uppercase transition-all duration-200 hover:border-[#0A0A0A]/30 hover:text-[#0A0A0A]/60">
            Apply →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
